OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784224105
OL,3,CRapist caught on camera before
OL,4,Csexually assaulting man in Leicester
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FA rapist who sexually assaulted a man
OL,8,Fin a park, has been convicted after
OL,9,Fwitnesses caught him in on camera.
OL,11,FIslamuddin Talash, 43, approached the
OL,12,Fvictim who was sitting on a bench in
OL,13,FAbbey Park, in Leicester on Monday,
OL,14,FOctober 9, 2023.
OL,16,FThey briefly spoke about bikes and
OL,17,FTalash offered to take the victim to
OL,18,Fhis flat to look at a bike he would
OL,19,Fgive to him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
