FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784224105
OL,3,CRapist caught on camera before
OL,4,Csexually assaulting man in Leicester
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FThey walked through the park when
OL,8,FTalash took the 20-year-old victim
OL,9,Finto a bush and raped him.
OL,11,FShortly before the assault, two
OL,12,Fteenage boys were suspicious of
OL,13,FTalash's behaviour so filmed him on
OL,14,Ftheir mobile phone.
OL,16,FThe witnesses kept an eye on Talash
OL,17,Fand approached the bush when the
OL,18,Foffender ran away and the witnesses
OL,19,Fwere able to help the victim.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784224105
OL,3,CRapist caught on camera before
OL,4,Csexually assaulting man in Leicester
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FAn officer working on the
OL,8,Finvestigation was walking through the
OL,9,Fpark and noticed a man matching
OL,10,FTalash's description based on pictures
OL,11,Fcaptured by the young witnesses.
OL,13,FTalash, from Smethwick, was found
OL,14,Fguilty of rape at Leicester Crown
OL,15,FCourt and jailed for six years. He is
OL,16,Fplaced on the sex offender register
OL,17,Findefinitely.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
