PN,34404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784224105
OL,3,CRapist caught on camera before
OL,4,Csexually assaulting man in Leicester
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Sarah Jones from
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police said: "The
OL,9,Factions of the witnesses on that day
OL,10,Fwere crucial in the investigation,
OL,11,Fthey did absolutely the right thing by
OL,12,Facting on their suspicions.
OL,14,F"The two boys were able to provide an
OL,15,Fimage and footage which assisted
OL,16,Fofficers in getting a positive
OL,17,Fidentification."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
